{"tid":1318454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【沙田+上水檢討】物資人鏈有幾點必須改善","createTime":"2019-07-15T02:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T15:36:32.000Z","uid":131691,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c25c9441fa3686156b90157ff8fcc20454007b8f","tid":1318454,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:49:39.000Z","msg":"1，好重要：人同人之間要有起碼成隻手嘅距離<br />\n或甚至每人「大」字pose，拳頭對拳頭，咁就啱啱好<br />\n沙田一役出現700+ m物資人鏈，但係企得好密<br />\n行路傳仲快過人鏈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每一次轉手就係浪費咗嘅時間，所以請保持空間<br />\n<br />\n2，物資手勢要熟，仲有人直遮=索帶<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KQS3NBT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKQS3NBT.gif&h=bde75337&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢個圖已經有啲outdated，盾/紙皮等已經近日出現咗<br />\n<br />\n3，唔好玩手機<br />\n有人好hea咁一隻手篤機，一隻手傳嘢<br />\n喂，你咁樣其實拖慢咗成條人鏈<br />\n因爲你變咗個樽頸位<br />\n<br />\n4，幫手傳訊息<br />\n有好多人，人鏈內或人鏈週邊<br />\n都係見到物資手勢後，淨係企喺度<br />\n喂，幫手傳訊息啦<br />\n你估次次都會好似沙田咁「天降物資」咩"},{"pid":"a3c3007d00f0eb3a38e7b8a756946b451ec4e6b5","tid":1318454,"uid":131691,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:50:06.000Z","msg":"有漏請回覆呢個post"},{"pid":"a2e84d74e2919cb4f6948cf4f06b51521bff82cc","tid":1318454,"uid":187796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:51:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74e5524e6a857857d0dfc67429a87d7b7146f652","tid":1318454,"uid":61282,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:52:20.000Z","msg":"真係太密，其實傳得好慢"},{"pid":"8957bcdb7dec3d6dc992ff23058411c46cb20e48","tid":1318454,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:52:31.000Z","msg":"推畀和理非朋友"},{"pid":"bbc4f02fd3193347fbefa6f29e1c2c7185d0325f","tid":1318454,"uid":131691,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"74e5524e6a857857d0dfc67429a87d7b7146f652","tid":1318454,"uid":61282,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:52:20.000Z","msg":"真係太密，其實傳得好慢"},